                                var ut = O & U ^ ~O & X
                                    , lt = I & K ^ ~I & L
                                    , dt = C & D ^ C & M ^ D & M
                                    , pt = R & E ^ R & F ^ E & F
                                    , _t = (C >>> 28 | R << 4) ^ (C << 30 | R >>> 2) ^ (C << 25 | R >>> 7)
                                    , vt = (R >>> 28 | C << 4) ^ (R << 30 | C >>> 2) ^ (R << 25 | C >>> 7)
                                    , yt = (O >>> 14 | I << 18) ^ (O >>> 18 | I << 14) ^ (O << 23 | I >>> 9)
                                    , gt = (I >>> 14 | O << 18) ^ (I >>> 18 | O << 14) ^ (I << 23 | O >>> 9)
                                    , Bt = h[N]
                                    , wt = Bt.high
                                    , kt = Bt.low
                                    , xt = j + gt
                                    , bt = T + yt + (xt >>> 0 < j >>> 0 ? 1 : 0)
                                    , mt = (xt = xt + lt,
                                    bt = bt + ut + (xt >>> 0 < lt >>> 0 ? 1 : 0),
                                    xt = xt + kt,
                                    bt = bt + wt + (xt >>> 0 < kt >>> 0 ? 1 : 0),
                                    xt = xt + Z,
                                    bt = bt + q + (xt >>> 0 < Z >>> 0 ? 1 : 0),
                                vt + pt)
                                    , St = _t + dt + (mt >>> 0 < vt >>> 0 ? 1 : 0);
                                T = X,
                                    j = L,
                                    X = U,
                                    L = K,
                                    U = O,
                                    K = I,
                                    I = W + xt | 0,
                                    O = P + bt + (I >>> 0 < W >>> 0 ? 1 : 0) | 0,
                                    P = M,
                                    W = F,
                                    M = D,
                                    F = E,
                                    D = C,
                                    E = R,
                                    R = xt + mt | 0,
                                    C = bt + St + (R >>> 0 < xt >>> 0 ? 1 : 0) | 0
                            }
                            p = n.low = p + R,
                                n.high = d + C + (p >>> 0 < R >>> 0 ? 1 : 0),
                                v = i.low = v + E,
                                i.high = _ + D + (v >>> 0 < E >>> 0 ? 1 : 0),
                                g = o.low = g + F,
                                o.high = y + M + (g >>> 0 < F >>> 0 ? 1 : 0),
                                w = c.low = w + W,
                                c.high = B + P + (w >>> 0 < W >>> 0 ? 1 : 0),
                                x = s.low = x + I,
                                s.high = k + O + (x >>> 0 < I >>> 0 ? 1 : 0),
                                m = a.low = m + K,
                                a.high = b + U + (m >>> 0 < K >>> 0 ? 1 : 0),
                                A = u.low = A + L,
                                u.high = S + X + (A >>> 0 < L >>> 0 ? 1 : 0),
                                z = l.low = z + j,
                                l.high = H + T + (z >>> 0 < j >>> 0 ? 1 : 0)
                        },
                        _doFinalize: function() {
                            var t = this._data
                                , e = t.words
                                , r = 8 * this._nDataBytes
                                , n = 8 * t.sigBytes;
                            e[n >>> 5] |= 128 << 24 - n % 32,
                                e[30 + (n + 128 >>> 10 << 5)] = Math.floor(r / 4294967296),
                                e[31 + (n + 128 >>> 10 << 5)] = r,
                                t.sigBytes = 4 * e.length,
                                this._process();
                            var i = this._hash.toX32();
                            return i
                        },
                        clone: function() {
                            var t = n.clone.call(this);
                            return t._hash = this._hash.clone(),
                                t
                        },
                        blockSize: 32
                    });
                    e.SHA512 = n._createHelper(u),
                        e.HmacSHA512 = n._createHmacHelper(u)
                }(),
                    t.SHA512
            }
        ))
    },

                            return t._hash = this._hash.clone(),

                    function p(t, e, r) {
                        return t ^ e ^ r
                    }
                    function _(t, e, r) {
                        return t & e | ~t & r
                    }
                    function v(t, e, r) {
                        return (t | ~e) ^ r

                        t.clamp(),
                            t.sigBytes += r - (t.sigBytes % r || r)
                    },
                    unpad: function(t) {

                            , r = t.sigBytes - 1;
                        for (r = t.sigBytes - 1; r >= 0; r--)
                            if (e[r >>> 2] >>> 24 - r % 4 * 8 & 255) {
                                t.sigBytes = r + 1;
                                break
                            }
                    }
                },

    "707d": function(t, e, r) {
        (function(e, n, i) {
                t.exports = n(r("c46e"), r("d438"))
            }
        )(0, (function(t) {
                return function(e) {
                    var r = t
                        , n = r.lib
                        , i = n.WordArray
                        , o = n.Hasher
                        , c = r.x64
                        , s = c.Word
                        , a = r.algo
                        , h = []
                        , f = []
                        , u = [];
                    (function() {
                            for (var t = 1, e = 0, r = 0; r < 24; r++) {
                                h[t + 5 * e] = (r + 1) * (r + 2) / 2 % 64;
                                var n = e % 5
                                    , i = (2 * t + 3 * e) % 5;
                                t = n,
                                    e = i
                            }
                            for (t = 0; t < 5; t++)
                                for (e = 0; e < 5; e++)
                                    f[t + 5 * e] = e + (2 * t + 3 * e) % 5 * 5;
                            for (var o = 1, c = 0; c < 24; c++) {
                                for (var a = 0, l = 0, d = 0; d < 7; d++) {
                                    if (1 & o) {
                                        var p = (1 << d) - 1;
                                        p < 32 ? l ^= 1 << p : a ^= 1 << p - 32
                                    }
                                    128 & o ? o = o << 1 ^ 113 : o <<= 1
                                }
                                u[c] = s.create(a, l)
                            }
                        }
                    )();

                    (function() {
                            for (var t = 0; t < 25; t++)
                                l[t] = s.create()
                        }
                    )();
                    var d = a.SHA3 = o.extend({
                        cfg: o.cfg.extend({
                            outputLength: 512
                        }),
                        _doReset: function() {
                            for (var t = this._state = [], e = 0; e < 25; e++)
                                t[e] = new s.init;
                            this.blockSize = (1600 - 2 * this.cfg.outputLength) / 32
                        },
                        _doProcessBlock: function(t, e) {
                            for (var r = this._state, n = this.blockSize / 2, i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                                var o = t[e + 2 * i]
                                    , c = t[e + 2 * i + 1];
                                o = 16711935 & (o << 8 | o >>> 24) | 4278255360 & (o << 24 | o >>> 8),
                                    c = 16711935 & (c << 8 | c >>> 24) | 4278255360 & (c << 24 | c >>> 8);
                                var s = r[i];
                                s.high ^= c,
                                    s.low ^= o
                            }
                            for (var a = 0; a < 24; a++) {
                                for (var d = 0; d < 5; d++) {
                                    for (var p = 0, _ = 0, v = 0; v < 5; v++) {
                                        s = r[d + 5 * v];
                                        p ^= s.high,
                                            _ ^= s.low
                                    }
                                    var y = l[d];
                                    y.high = p,
                                        y.low = _
                                }
                                for (d = 0; d < 5; d++) {
                                    var g = l[(d + 4) % 5]
                                        , B = l[(d + 1) % 5]
                                        , w = B.high
                                        , k = B.low;
                                    for (p = g.high ^ (w << 1 | k >>> 31),
                                             _ = g.low ^ (k << 1 | w >>> 31),
                                             v = 0; v < 5; v++) {
                                        s = r[d + 5 * v];
                                        s.high ^= p,
                                            s.low ^= _
                                    }
                                }
                                for (var x = 1; x < 25; x++) {
                                    s = r[x];
                                    var b = s.high

                                        _ = m << S | b >>> 32 - S) : (p = m << S - 32 | b >>> 64 - S,
                                        _ = b << S - 32 | m >>> 64 - S);

                                    A.high = p,
                                        A.low = _
                                }
                                var H = l[0]
                                    , z = r[0];
                                H.high = z.high,
                                    H.low = z.low;
                                for (d = 0; d < 5; d++)
                                    for (v = 0; v < 5; v++) {
                                        x = d + 5 * v,
                                            s = r[x];
                                        var C = l[x]
                                            , R = l[(d + 1) % 5 + 5 * v]
                                            , D = l[(d + 2) % 5 + 5 * v];
                                        s.high = C.high ^ ~R.high & D.high,
                                            s.low = C.low ^ ~R.low & D.low
                                    }
                                s = r[0];
                                var E = u[a];
                                s.high ^= E.high,
                                    s.low ^= E.low
                            }
                        },
                        _doFinalize: function() {
                            var t = this._data
                                , r = t.words
                                , n = (this._nDataBytes,

                            l && t && (e ? r.default.set(t, e, r.default.clone(r.default.get(l, e), !0)) : r.default.destructuring(t, r.default.clone(l, !0)))
                        }
                    }
                )),
                    t ? this.$nextTick() : this.reloadData(o)
            },

            },

            },

            updateAfterFullData: function() {
                var t = this
                    , e = this.tableFullColumn
                    , n = this.tableFullData
                    , i = this.filterOpts

                    , l = i.remote

                        var e = t.sortable
                            , n = t.order

                        if (!l && r && r.length) {

                                        i.push(t.value))

                        })
                    }

                                                $table: t
                                            })
                                        }
                                    )) : c ? c({
                                        options: u,

                                    }) : o.indexOf(r.default.get(e, i.property)) > -1
                                }
                                return !0
                            }
                        ))
                    }
                )));
                var m = v[0];
                if (!u && m)
                    if (f) {
                        var g = f({
                            data: h,

                            property: m.property,
                            order: m.order,
                            sortList: v,
                            $table: this
                        });
                        h = r.default.isArray(g) ? g : h
                    } else {
                        var b;
                        if (d)
                            h = r.default.orderBy(h, v.map((function(e) {
                                    var n = e.column
                                        , r = e.order;
                                    return [X(t, n), r]
                                }
                            )));
                        else
                            r.default.isArray(m.sortBy) && (b = m.sortBy.map((function(t) {
                                    return [t, m.order]
                                }
                            ))),

                                        var n = e.column
                                            , r = e.order;
                                        return [X(t, n), r]
                                    }
                                )))
                    }
                return this.afterFullData = h,
                    h
            },

            restoreCustomStorage: function() {
                var t = this.id
                    , e = this.collectColumn
                    , n = this.customConfig

                    , o = i.storage
                    , a = !0 === i.storage
                    , l = a || o && o.resizable
                    , c = a || o && o.visible;
                if (n && (l || c)) {
                    var u = {};
                    if (!t)
                        return void s.UtilTools.error("vxe.error.reqProp", ["id"]);
                    if (l) {
                        var f = F(D)[t];
                        f && r.default.each(f, (function(t, e) {
                                u[e] = {
                                    field: e,

                                }
                            }
                        ))

                        if (d) {

                                , v = h[1] ? h[1].split(",") : [];

                                        field: t,
                                        visible: !1
                                    }
                                }
                            )),
                                v.forEach((function(t) {
                                        u[t] ? u[t].visible = !0 : u[t] = {
                                            field: t,
                                            visible: !0
                                        }
                                    }
                                ))
                        }
                    }
                    var m = {};
                    r.default.eachTree(e, (function(t) {
                            var e = t.getKey();
                            e && (m[e] = t)
                        }
                    )),
                        r.default.each(u, (function(t, e) {
                                var n = t.visible
                                    , i = t.resizeWidth
                                    , o = m[e];
                                o && (r.default.isNumber(i) && (o.resizeWidth = i),
                                r.default.isBoolean(n) && (o.visible = n))
                            }
                        ))
                }
            },
            saveCustomVisible: function() {

            },

            refreshColumn: function() {

            parseColumns: function() {
                var t = this
                    , e = []
                    , n = []
                    , i = []
                    , o = this.collectColumn
                    , a = this.tableFullColumn
                    , l = this.isGroup
                    , c = this.columnStore
                    , u = this.sXOpts
                    , f = this.scrollXStore;
                if (l) {
                    var d = []
                        , h = []
                        , p = [];
                    r.default.eachTree(o, (function(t, o, a, l, c) {
                            var u = T(t);
                            c && c.fixed && (t.fixed = c.fixed),
                            c && t.fixed !== c.fixed && s.UtilTools.error("vxe.error.groupFixed"),
                                u ? t.visible = !!r.default.findTree(t.children, (function(t) {
                                        return T(t) ? null : t.visible
                                    }
                                )) : t.visible && ("left" === t.fixed ? e.push(t) : "right" === t.fixed ? i.push(t) : n.push(t))
                        }
                    )),
                        o.forEach((function(t) {
                                t.visible && ("left" === t.fixed ? d.push(t) : "right" === t.fixed ? p.push(t) : h.push(t))
                            }
                        )),
                        this.tableGroupColumn = d.concat(h).concat(p)
                } else
                    a.forEach((function(t) {
                            t.visible && ("left" === t.fixed ? e.push(t) : "right" === t.fixed ? i.push(t) : n.push(t))
                        }
                    ));
                var v = e.concat(n).concat(i)
                    , m = u.enabled && u.gt > -1 && u.gt < a.length;
                if (this.hasFixedColumn = e.length > 0 || i.length > 0,
                    Object.assign(c, {
                        leftList: e,
                        centerList: n,
                        rightList: i
                    }),
                m && l && (m = !1),
                    m) {
                    0;
                    var g = H(this)
                        , b = g.visibleSize;
                    f.startIndex = 0,
                        f.endIndex = b,
                        f.visibleSize = b
                }
                return v.length === this.visibleColumn.length && this.visibleColumn.every((function(t, e) {
                        return t === v[e]
                    }
                )) || (this.clearMergeCells(),
                    this.clearMergeFooterItems()),
                    this.scrollXLoad = m,
                    this.visibleColumn = v,
                    this.handleTableColumn(),
                    this.updateFooter().then((function() {
                            return t.recalculate()
                        }
                    )).then((function() {
                            return t.updateCellAreas(),
                                t.recalculate()
                        }
                    ))
            },
            analyColumnWidth: function() {
                var t = this.columnOpts
                    , e = t.width
                    , n = t.minWidth
                    , r = []
                    , i = []
                    , o = []
                    , a = []
                    , l = []
                    , c = [];
                this.tableFullColumn.forEach((function(t) {
                        e && !t.width && (t.width = e),
                        n && !t.minWidth && (t.minWidth = n),
                        t.visible && (t.resizeWidth ? r.push(t) : s.DomTools.isPx(t.width) ? i.push(t) : s.DomTools.isScale(t.width) ? a.push(t) : s.DomTools.isPx(t.minWidth) ? o.push(t) : s.DomTools.isScale(t.minWidth) ? l.push(t) : c.push(t))
                    }
                )),
                    Object.assign(this.columnStore, {
                        resizeList: r,
                        pxList: i,
                        pxMinList: o,
                        scaleList: a,
                        scaleMinList: l,
                        autoList: c
                    })
            },
            refreshScroll: function() {
                var t = this.lastScrollLeft
                    , e = this.lastScrollTop
                    , n = this.$refs
                    , r = n.tableBody
                    , i = n.leftBody
                    , o = n.rightBody
                    , a = n.tableFooter
                    , s = r ? r.$el : null
                    , c = i ? i.$el : null
                    , f = o ? o.$el : null
                    , d = a ? a.$el : null;
                if (t || e)
                    return (0,
                        l.restoreScrollLocation)(this, t, e);
                (0,
                    u.setScrollTop)(s, e),
                    (0,
                        u.setScrollTop)(c, e),
                    (0,
                        u.setScrollTop)(f, e),
                    (0,
                        u.setScrollLeft)(d, t)
            },
            recalculate: function(t) {
                var e = this
                    , n = this.$refs
                    , r = n.tableBody
                    , i = n.tableHeader
                    , o = n.tableFooter
                    , a = r ? r.$el : null
                    , s = i ? i.$el : null
                    , l = o ? o.$el : null;
                return a && (this.autoCellWidth(s, a, l),
                !0 === t) ? this.computeScrollLoad().then((function() {
                        return e.autoCellWidth(s, a, l),
                            e.computeScrollLoad()
                    }
                )) : this.computeScrollLoad()
            },
            autoCellWidth: function(t, e, n) {
                var r = 0
                    , i = 40
                    , o = e.clientWidth - 1
                    , a = o
                    , s = a / 100
                    , l = this.fit
                    , c = this.columnStore
                    , u = c.resizeList
                    , f = c.pxMinList
                    , d = c.pxList
                    , h = c.scaleList
                    , p = c.scaleMinList
                    , v = c.autoList;
                if (f.forEach((function(t) {
                        var e = parseInt(t.minWidth);
                        r += e,
                            t.renderWidth = e
                    }
                )),
                    p.forEach((function(t) {
                            var e = Math.floor(parseInt(t.minWidth) * s);
                            r += e,
                                t.renderWidth = e
                        }
                    )),
                    h.forEach((function(t) {
                            var e = Math.floor(parseInt(t.width) * s);
                            r += e,
                                t.renderWidth = e
                        }
                    )),
                    d.forEach((function(t) {
                            var e = parseInt(t.width);
                            r += e,
                                t.renderWidth = e
                        }
                    )),
                    u.forEach((function(t) {
                            var e = parseInt(t.resizeWidth);
                            r += e,
                                t.renderWidth = e
                        }
                    )),
                    a -= r,
                    s = a > 0 ? Math.floor(a / (p.length + f.length + v.length)) : 0,
                    l ? a > 0 && p.concat(f).forEach((function(t) {
                            r += s,
                                t.renderWidth += s
                        }
                    )) : s = i,
                    v.forEach((function(t) {
                            var e = Math.max(s, i);
                            t.renderWidth = e,
                                r += e
                        }
                    )),
                    l) {
                    var m = h.concat(p).concat(f).concat(v)
                        , g = m.length - 1;
                    if (g > 0) {
                        var b = o - r;
                        if (b > 0) {
                            while (b > 0 && g >= 0)
                                b--,
                                    m[g--].renderWidth++;
                            r = o
                        }
                    }
                }
                var x = e.offsetHeight
                    , y = e.scrollHeight > e.clientHeight;
                if (this.scrollbarWidth = y ? e.offsetWidth - e.clientWidth : 0,
                    this.overflowY = y,
                    this.tableWidth = r,
                    this.tableHeight = x,
                    t ? (this.headerHeight = t.clientHeight,
                        this.$nextTick((function() {
                                t && e && t.scrollLeft !== e.scrollLeft && (t.scrollLeft = e.scrollLeft)
                            }
                        ))) : this.headerHeight = 0,
                    n) {
                    var w = n.offsetHeight;
                    this.scrollbarHeight = Math.max(w - n.clientHeight, 0),
                        this.overflowX = r > n.clientWidth,
                        this.footerHeight = w
                } else
                    this.footerHeight = 0,
                        this.scrollbarHeight = Math.max(x - e.clientHeight, 0),
                        this.overflowX = r > o;
                this.updateHeight(),
                    this.parentHeight = Math.max(this.headerHeight + this.footerHeight + 20, this.getParentHeight()),
                this.overflowX && this.checkScrolling()
            },
            updateHeight: function() {
                this.customHeight = k(this, "height"),
                    this.customMaxHeight = k(this, "maxHeight")
            },
            updateStyle: function() {
                var t = this
                    , e = this.$refs
                    , n = this.isGroup
                    , i = this.fullColumnIdData
                    , o = this.tableColumn
                    , a = this.customHeight
                    , s = this.customMaxHeight
                    , l = this.border
                    , c = this.headerHeight
                    , f = this.showFooter
                    , d = this.showOverflow
                    , h = this.showHeaderOverflow
                    , p = this.showFooterOverflow
                    , v = this.footerHeight
                    , m = this.tableHeight
                    , g = this.tableWidth
                    , b = this.scrollbarHeight
                    , x = this.scrollbarWidth
                    , y = this.scrollXLoad
                    , w = this.scrollYLoad
                    , O = this.cellOffsetWidth
                    , S = this.columnStore
                    , C = this.elemStore
                    , T = this.editStore
                    , E = this.currentRow
                    , k = this.mouseConfig
                    , j = this.keyboardConfig
                    , I = this.keyboardOpts
                    , R = this.spanMethod
                    , $ = this.mergeList
                    , M = this.mergeFooterList
                    , A = this.footerSpanMethod
                    , D = this.isAllOverflow
                    , L = this.visibleColumn
                    , P = ["main", "left", "right"]
                    , _ = e.emptyPlaceholder
                    , N = C["main-body-wrapper"];
                return _ && (_.style.top = "".concat(c, "px"),
                    _.style.height = N ? "".concat(N.offsetHeight - b, "px") : ""),
                a > 0 && f && (a += b),
                    P.forEach((function(T, E) {
                            var k = E > 0 ? T : ""
                                , P = ["header", "body", "footer"]
                                , _ = S["".concat(k, "List")]
                                , N = e["".concat(k, "Container")];
                            P.forEach((function(e) {
                                    var E = C["".concat(T, "-").concat(e, "-wrapper")]
                                        , P = C["".concat(T, "-").concat(e, "-table")];
                                    if ("header" === e) {
                                        var F = g
                                            , B = !1;
                                        n || k && (y || h) && (B = !0),
                                        B && (o = _),
                                        (B || y) && (F = o.reduce((function(t, e) {
                                                return t + e.renderWidth
                                            }
                                        ), 0)),
                                        P && (P.style.width = F ? "".concat(F + x, "px") : "",
                                        u.browse.msie && r.default.arrayEach(P.querySelectorAll(".vxe-resizable"), (function(t) {
                                                t.style.height = "".concat(t.parentNode.offsetHeight, "px")
                                            }
                                        )));
                                        var z = C["".concat(T, "-").concat(e, "-repair")];
                                        z && (z.style.width = "".concat(g, "px"));
                                        var H = C["".concat(T, "-").concat(e, "-list")];
                                        n && H && r.default.arrayEach(H.querySelectorAll(".col--group"), (function(e) {
                                                var n = t.getColumnNode(e);
                                                if (n) {
                                                    var i = n.item
                                                        , o = i.showHeaderOverflow
                                                        , a = r.default.isBoolean(o) ? o : h
                                                        , s = "ellipsis" === a
                                                        , c = "title" === a
                                                        , u = !0 === a || "tooltip" === a

            getCheckboxIndeterminateRecords: function(t) {

            },
            handleDefaultSelectionChecked: function() {
                var t = this.fullDataRowIdData
                    , e = this.checkboxOpts
                    , n = e.checkAll
                    , r = e.checkRowKeys;
                if (n)
                    this.setAllCheckboxRow(!0);

                            t[e] && i.push(t[e].row)

                }
            },
            setCheckboxRow: function(t, e) {
                var n = this;

                            return n.handleSelectRow({
                                row: t
                            }, !!e)
                        }
                    )),

            },
            isCheckedByCheckboxRow: function(t) {
                var e = this.checkboxOpts.checkField;
                return e ? r.default.get(t, e) : this.selection.indexOf(t) > -1
            },
            isIndeterminateByCheckboxRow: function(t) {
                return this.treeIndeterminates.indexOf(t) > -1 && !this.isCheckedByCheckboxRow(t)
            },
            handleSelectRow: function(t, e) {
                var n = this
                    , i = t.row
                    , o = this.selection
                    , a = this.afterFullData
                    , s = this.treeConfig
                    , l = this.treeOpts
                    , c = this.treeIndeterminates
                    , u = this.checkboxOpts
                    , f = u.checkField
                    , d = u.checkStrictly
                    , h = u.checkMethod;
                if (f)
                    if (s && !d) {
                        -1 === e ? (-1 === c.indexOf(i) && c.push(i),
                            r.default.set(i, f, !1)) : r.default.eachTree([i], (function(t) {
                                i !== t && h && !h({
                                    row: t
                                }) || (r.default.set(t, f, e),
                                    r.default.remove(c, (function(e) {
                                            return e === t
                                        }
                                    )),
                                    n.handleCheckboxReserveRow(i, e))
                            }
                        ), l);
                        var p = r.default.findTree(a, (function(t) {
                                return t === i
                            }
                        ), l);
                        if (p && p.parent) {
                            var v, m = h ? p.items.filter((function(t) {
                                    return h({
                                        row: t
                                    })
                                }
                            )) : p.items, g = r.default.find(p.items, (function(t) {
                                    return c.indexOf(t) > -1
                                }
                            ));
                            if (g)
                                v = -1;
                            else {
                                var b = p.items.filter((function(t) {
                                        return r.default.get(t, f)
                                    }
                                ));
                                v = b.filter((function(t) {
                                        return m.indexOf(t) > -1
                                    }
                                )).length === m.length || !(!b.length && -1 !== e) && -1
                            }
                            return this.handleSelectRow({
                                row: p.parent
                            }, v)
                        }
                    } else
                        h && !h({
                            row: i
                        }) || (r.default.set(i, f, e),
                            this.handleCheckboxReserveRow(i, e));
                else if (s && !d) {
                    -1 === e ? (-1 === c.indexOf(i) && c.push(i),
                        r.default.remove(o, (function(t) {
                                return t === i
                            }
                        ))) : r.default.eachTree([i], (function(t) {
                            i !== t && h && !h({
                                row: t
                            }) || (e ? o.push(t) : r.default.remove(o, (function(e) {
                                    return e === t
                                }
                            )),
                                r.default.remove(c, (function(e) {
                                        return e === t
                                    }
                                )),
                                n.handleCheckboxReserveRow(i, e))
                        }
                    ), l);
                    var x = r.default.findTree(a, (function(t) {
                            return t === i
                        }
                    ), l);
                    if (x && x.parent) {
                        var y, w = h ? x.items.filter((function(t) {
                                return h({
                                    row: t
                                })
                            }
                        )) : x.items, O = r.default.find(x.items, (function(t) {
                                return c.indexOf(t) > -1
                            }
                        ));
                        if (O)
                            y = -1;
                        else {
                            var S = x.items.filter((function(t) {
                                    return o.indexOf(t) > -1
                                }
                            ));
                            y = S.filter((function(t) {
                                    return w.indexOf(t) > -1
                                }
                            )).length === w.length || !(!S.length && -1 !== e) && -1
                        }
                        return this.handleSelectRow({
                            row: x.parent
                        }, y)
                    }
                } else
                    h && !h({
                        row: i
                    }) || (e ? -1 === o.indexOf(i) && o.push(i) : r.default.remove(o, (function(t) {
                            return t === i
                        }
                    )),
                        this.handleCheckboxReserveRow(i, e));
                this.checkSelectionStatus()
            },

                            }

            },

                    }
                }
                return null
            },

            clearCurrentColumn: function() {

            checkValidate: function(t) {

            },

                var n = this;
                this.checkValidate("blur").catch((function(t) {
                        return t
                    }
                )).then((function() {
                        n.handleActived(e, t).then((function() {
                                return n.checkValidate("change")
                            }
                        )).catch((function(t) {
                                return t
                            }
                        ))
                    }
                ))
            },
            triggerCellClickEvent: function(t, e) {
                var n = this.highlightCurrentRow
                    , r = this.editStore
                    , i = this.radioOpts

                    , a = this.treeOpts

                    , w = g && $(t, y, "vxe-cell--radio").flag

                    , C = x && $(t, y, "vxe-table--expanded").flag;

                    c.isEnableConf)(s) && ("manual" === l.trigger ? f.args && f.row === h && p !== f.column && this.handleChangeCell(t, e) : f.args && h === f.row && p === f.column || ("click" === l.trigger || "dblclick" === l.trigger && "row" === l.mode && f.row === h) && this.handleChangeCell(t, e))),
                    this.emitEvent("cell-click", e, t)
            },

            },
            handleDefaultSort: function() {
                var t = this
                    , e = this.sortConfig
                    , n = this.sortOpts
                    , i = n.defaultSort;
                i && (r.default.isArray(i) || (i = [i]),
                i.length && ((e.multiple ? i : i.slice(0, 1)).forEach((function(e) {
                        var n = e.field
                            , r = e.order;
                        if (n && r) {
                            var i = t.getColumnByField(n);
                            i && i.sortable && (i.order = r,
                                i.sortTime = Date.now())
                        }
                    }
                )),
                n.remote || this.handleTableData(!0).then(this.updateStyle)))
            },
            triggerSortEvent: function(t, e, n) {
                var r = this.sortOpts
                    , i = e.property;
                if (e.sortable || e.remoteSort) {
                    n && e.order !== n ? this.sort({
                        field: i,
                        order: n
                    }) : this.clearSort(r.multiple ? e : null);
                    var o = {
                        column: e,
                        property: i,
                        order: e.order,
                        sortList: this.getSortColumns()
                    };
                    this.emitEvent("sort-change", o, t)
                }
            },
            sort: function(t, e) {
                var n, i = this, o = this.sortOpts, a = o.multiple, s = o.remote, l = o.orders;
                return t && r.default.isString(t) && (t = [{
                    field: t,
                    order: e
                }]),
                r.default.isArray(t) || (t = [t]),
                    t.length ? (a || G(this),
                        (a ? t : [t[0]]).forEach((function(t) {
                                var e = t.field
                                    , o = t.order
                                    , a = e;
                                r.default.isString(e) && (a = i.getColumnByField(e)),
                                a && (a.sortable || a.remoteSort) && (n || (n = a),
                                -1 === l.indexOf(o) && (o = N(i, a)),
                                a.order !== o && (a.order = o))
                            }
                        )),
                    (!s || n && n.remoteSort) && this.handleTableData(!0),
                        this.$nextTick().then(this.updateStyle)) : this.$nextTick()
            },
            clearSort: function(t) {
                var e = this.sortOpts;
                if (t) {
                    var n = (0,
                        l.handleFieldOrColumn)(this, t);
                    n && (n.order = null)
                } else
                    G(this);
                return e.remote || this.handleTableData(!0),
                    this.$nextTick().then(this.updateStyle)
            },
            getSortColumn: function() {
                return r.default.find(this.tableFullColumn, (function(t) {
                        return (t.sortable || t.remoteSort) && t.order
                    }
                ))
            },
            isSort: function(t) {
                if (t) {
                    var e = (0,
                        l.handleFieldOrColumn)(this, t);
                    return e && e.sortable && !!e.order
                }
                return this.getSortColumns().length > 0
            },
            getSortColumns: function() {
                var t = [];
                return this.tableFullColumn.forEach((function(e) {
                        var n = e.order;
                        (e.sortable || e.remoteSort) && n && t.push({
                            column: e,
                            property: e.property,
                            order: n
                        })
                    }
                )),
                    t
            },
            closeFilter: function() {
                return Object.assign(this.filterStore, {
                    isAllSelected: !1,
                    isIndeterminate: !1,
                    options: [],
                    visible: !1
                }),
                    this.$nextTick()
            },
            isFilter: function(t) {
                var e = (0,
                    l.handleFieldOrColumn)(this, t);
                return e ? e.filters && e.filters.some((function(t) {
                        return t.checked
                    }
                )) : this.getCheckedFilters().length > 0
            },
            isRowExpandLoaded: function(t) {
                var e = this.fullAllDataRowMap.get(t);
                return e && e.expandLoaded
            },
            clearRowExpandLoaded: function(t) {
                var e = this.expandOpts
                    , n = this.expandLazyLoadeds
                    , i = this.fullAllDataRowMap
                    , o = e.lazy

                    r.default.remove(n, (function(e) {
                            return t === e
                        }
                    ))),
                    this.$nextTick()
            },
            reloadExpandContent: function(t) {
                var e = this
                    , n = this.expandOpts
                    , r = this.expandLazyLoadeds
                    , i = n.lazy;

                        return e.handleAsyncRowExpand(t)
                    }
                )),
                    this.$nextTick()
            },
            triggerRowExpandEvent: function(t, e) {
                var n = this.expandOpts
                    , r = this.expandLazyLoadeds
                    , i = this.expandColumn
                    , o = e.row
                    , a = n.lazy;
                if (!a || -1 === r.indexOf(o)) {
                    var s = !this.isExpandByRow(o)
                        , l = this.getColumnIndex(i)
                        , c = this.getVMColumnIndex(i);
                    this.setRowExpand(o, s),
                        this.emitEvent("toggle-row-expand", {
                            expanded: s,
                            column: i,
                            columnIndex: l,
                            $columnIndex: c,
                            row: o,
                            rowIndex: this.getRowIndex(o),
                            $rowIndex: this.getVMRowIndex(o)
                        }, t)
                }
            },
            toggleRowExpand: function(t) {
                return this.setRowExpand(t, !this.isExpandByRow(t))
            },
            handleDefaultRowExpand: function() {
                var t = this.expandOpts
                    , e = this.fullDataRowIdData
                    , n = t.expandAll
                    , r = t.expandRowKeys;
                if (n)
                    this.setAllRowExpand(!0);
                else if (r) {
                    var i = [];
                    r.forEach((function(t) {
                            e[t] && i.push(e[t].row)
                        }
                    )),
                        this.setRowExpand(i, !0)
                }
            },
            setAllRowExpand: function(t) {
                return this.setRowExpand(this.expandOpts.lazy ? this.tableData : this.tableFullData, t)
            },
            handleAsyncRowExpand: function(t) {
                var e = this
                    , n = this.fullAllDataRowMap.get(t);
                return new Promise((function(i) {
                        e.expandLazyLoadeds.push(t),
                            e.expandOpts.loadMethod({
                                $table: e,
                                row: t,
                                rowIndex: e.getRowIndex(t),
                                $rowIndex: e.getVMRowIndex(t)
                            }).catch((function(t) {
                                    return t
                                }
                            )).then((function() {
                                    n.expandLoaded = !0,
                                        r.default.remove(e.expandLazyLoadeds, (function(e) {
                                                return e === t
                                            }
                                        )),
                                        e.rowExpandeds.push(t),
                                        i(e.$nextTick().then(e.recalculate))
                                }
                            ))
                    }
                ))
            },
            setRowExpand: function(t, e) {
                var n = this
                    , i = this.fullAllDataRowMap
                    , o = this.expandLazyLoadeds
                    , a = this.expandOpts
                    , s = this.expandColumn
                    , l = this.rowExpandeds
                    , c = a.reserve
                    , u = a.lazy
                    , f = a.accordion
                    , d = a.toggleMethod
                    , h = []
                    , p = this.getColumnIndex(s)
                    , v = this.getVMColumnIndex(s);
                if (t) {
                    r.default.isArray(t) || (t = [t]),
                    f && (l = [],
                        t = t.slice(t.length - 1, t.length));
                    var m = d ? t.filter((function(t) {
                            return d({
                                expanded: e,
                                column: s,
                                columnIndex: p,
                                $columnIndex: v,
                                row: t,
                                rowIndex: n.getRowIndex(t),
                                $rowIndex: n.getVMRowIndex(t)
                            })
                        }
                    )) : t;
                    e ? m.forEach((function(t) {
                            if (-1 === l.indexOf(t)) {
                                var e = i.get(t)
                                    , r = u && !e.expandLoaded && -1 === o.indexOf(t);
                                r ? h.push(n.handleAsyncRowExpand(t)) : l.push(t)
                            }
                        }
                    )) : r.default.remove(l, (function(t) {
                            return m.indexOf(t) > -1
                        }
                    )),
                    c && m.forEach((function(t) {
                            return n.handleRowExpandReserve(t, e)
                        }
                    ))
                }
                return this.rowExpandeds = l,
                    Promise.all(h).then(this.recalculate)
            },
            isExpandByRow: function(t) {
                return this.rowExpandeds.indexOf(t) > -1
            },
            clearRowExpand: function() {
                var t = this
                    , e = this.expandOpts
                    , n = this.rowExpandeds
                    , r = this.tableFullData
                    , i = e.reserve
                    , o = n.length;
                return this.rowExpandeds = [],
                i && r.forEach((function(e) {
                        return t.handleRowExpandReserve(e, !1)
                    }
                )),
                    this.$nextTick().then((function() {
                            o && t.recalculate()
                        }
                    ))
            },
            clearRowExpandReserve: function() {
                return this.rowExpandedReserveRowMap = {},
                    this.$nextTick()
            },
            handleRowExpandReserve: function(t, e) {
                var n = this.rowExpandedReserveRowMap
                    , r = this.expandOpts;
                if (r.reserve) {
                    var i = O(this, t);
                    e ? n[i] = t : n[i] && delete n[i]
                }
            },
            getRowExpandRecords: function() {
                return this.rowExpandeds.slice(0)
            },
            getTreeExpandRecords: function() {
                return this.treeExpandeds.slice(0)
            },
            getTreeStatus: function() {
                return this.treeConfig ? {
                    config: this.treeOpts,
                    rowExpandeds: this.getTreeExpandRecords()
                } : null
            },
            isTreeExpandLoaded: function(t) {
                var e = this.fullAllDataRowMap.get(t);
                return e && e.treeLoaded
            },
            clearTreeExpandLoaded: function(t) {
                var e = this.treeOpts
                    , n = this.treeExpandeds
                    , i = this.fullAllDataRowMap
                    , o = e.lazy
                    , a = i.get(t);
                return o && a && (a.treeLoaded = !1,
                    r.default.remove(n, (function(e) {
                            return t === e
                        }
                    ))),
                    this.$nextTick()
            },
            reloadTreeChilds: function(t) {
                var e = this
                    , n = this.treeOpts
                    , r = this.treeLazyLoadeds
                    , i = n.lazy
                    , o = n.hasChild;
                return i && t[o] && -1 === r.indexOf(t) && this.clearTreeExpandLoaded(t).then((function() {
                        return e.handleAsyncTreeExpandChilds(t)
                    }
                )),
                    this.$nextTick()
            },
            triggerTreeExpandEvent: function(t, e) {
                var n = this.treeOpts
                    , r = this.treeLazyLoadeds
                    , i = e.row
                    , o = e.column
                    , a = n.lazy;
                if (!a || -1 === r.indexOf(i)) {
                    var s = !this.isTreeExpandByRow(i)
                        , l = this.getColumnIndex(o)
                        , c = this.getVMColumnIndex(o);
                    this.setTreeExpand(i, s),
                        this.emitEvent("toggle-tree-expand", {
                            expanded: s,
                            column: o,
                            columnIndex: l,
                            $columnIndex: c,
                            row: i
                        }, t)
                }
            },
            toggleTreeExpand: function(t) {
                return this.setTreeExpand(t, !this.isTreeExpandByRow(t))
            },
            handleDefaultTreeExpand: function() {
                var t = this.treeConfig
                    , e = this.treeOpts
                    , n = this.tableFullData;
                if (t) {
                    var i = e.expandAll
                        , o = e.expandRowKeys;
                    if (i)
                        this.setAllTreeExpand(!0);
                    else if (o) {
                        var a = []
                            , s = S(this);
                        o.forEach((function(t) {
                                var i = r.default.findTree(n, (function(e) {
                                        return t === r.default.get(e, s)
                                    }
                                ), e);
                                i && a.push(i.item)
                            }
                        )),
                            this.setTreeExpand(a, !0)
                    }
                }
            },
            handleAsyncTreeExpandChilds: function(t) {
                var e = this
                    , n = this.fullAllDataRowMap
                    , i = this.treeExpandeds
                    , o = this.treeOpts
                    , a = this.treeLazyLoadeds
                    , s = this.checkboxOpts
                    , l = o.loadMethod
                    , c = s.checkStrictly
                    , u = n.get(t);
                return new Promise((function(n) {
                        a.push(t),
                            l({
                                $table: e,
                                row: t
                            }).catch((function() {
                                    return []
                                }
                            )).then((function(o) {
                                    u.treeLoaded = !0,
                                        r.default.remove(a, (function(e) {
                                                return e === t
                                            }
                                        )),
                                    r.default.isArray(o) || (o = []),
                                    o && e.loadChildren(t, o).then((function(n) {
                                            n.length && -1 === i.indexOf(t) && i.push(t),
                                            !c && e.isCheckedByCheckboxRow(t) && e.setCheckboxRow(n, !0)
                                        }
                                    )),
                                        n(e.$nextTick().then(e.recalculate))
                                }
                            ))
                    }
                ))
            },
            setAllTreeExpand: function(t) {
                var e = this.tableFullData
                    , n = this.treeOpts
                    , i = n.lazy
                    , o = n.children
                    , a = [];
                return r.default.eachTree(e, (function(t) {
                        var e = t[o];
                        (i || e && e.length) && a.push(t)
                    }
                ), n),
                    this.setTreeExpand(a, t)
            },
            setTreeExpand: function(t, e) {
                var n = this
                    , i = this.fullAllDataRowMap
                    , o = this.tableFullData
                    , a = this.treeExpandeds
                    , s = this.treeOpts
                    , l = this.treeLazyLoadeds
                    , c = this.treeNodeColumn
                    , u = s.reserve
                    , f = s.lazy
                    , d = s.hasChild
                    , h = s.children
                    , p = s.accordion
                    , v = s.toggleMethod
                    , m = []
                    , g = this.getColumnIndex(c)
                    , b = this.getVMColumnIndex(c);
                if (t && (r.default.isArray(t) || (t = [t]),
                    t.length)) {
                    var x = v ? t.filter((function(t) {
                            return v({
                                expanded: e,
                                column: c,
                                columnIndex: g,
                                $columnIndex: b,
                                row: t
                            })
                        }
                    )) : t;
                    if (p) {
                        x = x.length ? [x[x.length - 1]] : [];
                        var y = r.default.findTree(o, (function(t) {
                                return t === x[0]
                            }
                        ), s);
                        y && r.default.remove(a, (function(t) {
                                return y.items.indexOf(t) > -1
                            }
                        ))
                    }
                    return e ? x.forEach((function(t) {
                            if (-1 === a.indexOf(t)) {
                                var e = i.get(t)
                                    , r = f && t[d] && !e.treeLoaded && -1 === l.indexOf(t);
                                r ? m.push(n.handleAsyncTreeExpandChilds(t)) : t[h] && t[h].length && a.push(t)
                            }
                        }
                    )) : r.default.remove(a, (function(t) {
                            return x.indexOf(t) > -1
                        }
                    )),
                    u && x.forEach((function(t) {
                            return n.handleTreeExpandReserve(t, e)
                        }
                    )),
                        Promise.all(m).then(this.recalculate)
                }
                return this.$nextTick()
            },
            isTreeExpandByRow: function(t) {
                return this.treeExpandeds.indexOf(t) > -1
            },
            clearTreeExpand: function() {
                var t = this
                    , e = this.treeOpts
                    , n = this.treeExpandeds
                    , i = this.tableFullData
                    , o = e.reserve
                    , a = n.length;
                return this.treeExpandeds = [],
                o && r.default.eachTree(i, (function(e) {
                        return t.handleTreeExpandReserve(e, !1)
                    }
                ), e),
                    this.$nextTick().then((function() {
                            a && t.recalculate()
                        }
                    ))
            },
            clearTreeExpandReserve: function() {
                return this.treeExpandedReserveRowMap = {},
                    this.$nextTick()
            },
            handleTreeExpandReserve: function(t, e) {
                var n = this.treeExpandedReserveRowMap
                    , r = this.treeOpts;
                if (r.reserve) {
                    var i = O(this, t);
                    e ? n[i] = t : n[i] && delete n[i]
                }
            },
            getScroll: function() {
                var t = this.$refs
                    , e = this.scrollXLoad
                    , n = this.scrollYLoad
                    , r = t.tableBody.$el;
                return {
                    virtualX: e,
                    virtualY: n,
                    scrollTop: r.scrollTop,
                    scrollLeft: r.scrollLeft
                }
            },
            triggerScrollXEvent: function() {
                this.loadScrollXData()
            },
            loadScrollXData: function() {
                var t = this.mergeList
                    , e = this.mergeFooterList
                    , n = this.scrollXStore
                    , r = n.startIndex
                    , i = n.endIndex
                    , o = n.offsetSize
                    , a = H(this)
                    , s = a.toVisibleIndex
                    , l = a.visibleSize
                    , c = {
                    startIndex: Math.max(0, s - 1 - o),
                    endIndex: s + l + o
                };
                W(t.concat(e), c, "col");
                var u = c.startIndex
                    , f = c.endIndex;
                (s <= r || s >= i - l - 1) && (r === u && i === f || (n.startIndex = u,
                    n.endIndex = f,
                    this.updateScrollXData())),
                    this.closeTooltip()
            },
            triggerScrollYEvent: function(t) {
                var e = this.scrollYStore
                    , n = e.adaptive
                    , r = e.offsetSize
                    , i = e.visibleSize;
                M && n && 2 * r + i <= 40 ? this.loadScrollYData(t) : this.debounceScrollY(t)
            },
            debounceScrollY: r.default.debounce((function(t) {
                    this.loadScrollYData(t)
                }
            ), A, {
                leading: !1,
                trailing: !0
            }),
            loadScrollYData: function(t) {
                var e = this.mergeList
                    , n = this.scrollYStore
                    , r = n.startIndex
                    , i = n.endIndex
                    , o = n.visibleSize
                    , a = n.offsetSize
                    , s = n.rowHeight
                    , l = t.currentTarget || t.target
                    , c = l.scrollTop
                    , u = Math.floor(c / s)
                    , f = {
                    startIndex: Math.max(0, u - 1 - a),
                    endIndex: u + o + a
                };
                W(e, f, "row");
                var d = f.startIndex
                    , h = f.endIndex;
                (u <= r || u >= i - o - 1) && (r === d && i === h || (n.startIndex = d,
                    n.endIndex = h,
                    this.updateScrollYData()))
            },
            computeScrollLoad: function() {
                var t = this;
                return this.$nextTick().then((function() {
                        var e = t.sYOpts
                            , n = t.sXOpts
                            , i = t.scrollXLoad
                            , o = t.scrollYLoad
                            , a = t.scrollXStore
                            , s = t.scrollYStore;
                        if (i) {
                            var l = H(t)
                                , c = l.visibleSize
                                , f = n.oSize ? r.default.toNumber(n.oSize) : u.browse.msie ? 10 : u.browse.edge ? 5 : 0;
                            a.offsetSize = f,
                                a.visibleSize = c,
                                a.endIndex = Math.max(a.startIndex + a.visibleSize + f, a.endIndex),
                                t.updateScrollXData()
                        } else
                            t.updateScrollXSpace();
                        var d = V(t)
                            , h = d.rowHeight
                            , p = d.visibleSize;
                        if (s.rowHeight = h,
                            o) {
                            var v = e.oSize ? r.default.toNumber(e.oSize) : u.browse.msie ? 20 : u.browse.edge ? 10 : 0;
                            s.offsetSize = v,
                                s.visibleSize = p,
                                s.endIndex = Math.max(s.startIndex + p + v, s.endIndex),
                                t.updateScrollYData()
                        } else
                            t.updateScrollYSpace();
                        t.rowHeight = h,
                            t.$nextTick(t.updateStyle)
                    }
                ))
            },
            handleTableColumn: function() {
                var t = this.scrollXLoad
                    , e = this.visibleColumn
                    , n = this.scrollXStore;
                this.tableColumn = t ? e.slice(n.startIndex, n.endIndex) : e.slice(0)
            },
            updateScrollXData: function() {
                this.handleTableColumn(),
                    this.updateScrollXSpace()
            },
            updateScrollXSpace: function() {
                var t = this.$refs
                    , e = this.elemStore
                    , n = this.visibleColumn
                    , r = this.scrollXStore
                    , i = this.scrollXLoad
                    , o = this.tableWidth
                    , a = this.scrollbarWidth
                    , s = t.tableHeader
                    , l = t.tableBody
                    , c = t.tableFooter
                    , u = l ? l.$el : null;
                if (u) {
                    var f = s ? s.$el : null
                        , d = c ? c.$el : null
                        , h = f ? f.querySelector(".vxe-table--header") : null
                        , p = u.querySelector(".vxe-table--body")
                        , v = d ? d.querySelector(".vxe-table--footer") : null
                        , m = n.slice(0, r.startIndex).reduce((function(t, e) {
                            return t + e.renderWidth
                        }
                    ), 0)
                        , g = "";
                    i && (g = "".concat(m, "px")),
                    h && (h.style.marginLeft = g),
                        p.style.marginLeft = g,
                    v && (v.style.marginLeft = g);
                    var b = ["main"];
                    b.forEach((function(t) {
                            var n = ["header", "body", "footer"];
                            n.forEach((function(n) {
                                    var r = e["".concat(t, "-").concat(n, "-xSpace")];
                                    r && (r.style.width = i ? "".concat(o + ("header" === n ? a : 0), "px") : "")
                                }
                            ))
                        }
                    )),
                        this.$nextTick(this.updateStyle)
                }
            },
            updateScrollYData: function() {
                this.handleTableData(),
                    this.updateScrollYSpace()
            },
            updateScrollYSpace: function() {
                var t = this.elemStore
                    , e = this.scrollYStore
                    , n = this.scrollYLoad
                    , r = this.afterFullData
                    , i = e.startIndex
                    , o = e.rowHeight
                    , a = r.length * o
                    , s = Math.max(0, i * o)
                    , l = ["main", "left", "right"]
                    , c = ""
                    , u = "";
                n && (c = "".concat(s, "px"),
                    u = "".concat(a, "px")),
                    l.forEach((function(e) {
                            var n = ["header", "body", "footer"]
                                , r = t["".concat(e, "-body-table")];
                            r && (r.style.marginTop = c),
                                n.forEach((function(n) {
                                        var r = t["".concat(e, "-").concat(n, "-ySpace")];
                                        r && (r.style.height = u)
                                    }
                                ))
                        }
                    )),
                    this.$nextTick(this.updateStyle)
            },
            scrollTo: function(t, e) {
                var n = this
                    , i = this.$refs
                    , o = i.tableBody
                    , a = i.rightBody
                    , s = i.tableFooter
                    , l = o ? o.$el : null
                    , c = a ? a.$el : null
                    , f = s ? s.$el : null;
                return r.default.isNumber(t) && (0,
                    u.setScrollLeft)(f || l, t),
                r.default.isNumber(e) && (0,
                    u.setScrollTop)(c || l, e),
                    this.scrollXLoad || this.scrollYLoad ? new Promise((function(t) {
                            return setTimeout((function() {
                                    return t(n.$nextTick())
                                }
                            ), 50)
                        }
                    )) : this.$nextTick()
            },
            scrollToRow: function(t, e) {
                var n = [];
                return t && (this.treeConfig ? n.push(this.scrollToTreeRow(t)) : n.push(s.DomTools.rowToVisible(this, t))),
                e && n.push(this.scrollToColumn(e)),
                    Promise.all(n)
            },
            scrollToColumn: function(t) {
                var e = (0,
                    l.handleFieldOrColumn)(this, t);
                return e && this.fullColumnMap.has(e) ? s.DomTools.colToVisible(this, e) : this.$nextTick()
            },
            scrollToTreeRow: function(t) {
                var e = this
                    , n = this.tableFullData
                    , i = this.treeConfig
                    , o = this.treeOpts
                    , a = [];
                if (i) {
                    var l = r.default.findTree(n, (function(e) {
                            return e === t
                        }
                    ), o);
                    if (l) {
                        var c = l.nodes;
                        c.forEach((function(t, n) {
                                n < c.length - 1 && !e.isTreeExpandByRow(t) && a.push(e.setTreeExpand(t, !0))
                            }
                        ))
                    }
                }
                return Promise.all(a).then((function() {
                        return s.DomTools.rowToVisible(e, t)
                    }
                ))
            },
            clearScroll: function() {
                var t = this.$refs
                    , e = this.scrollXStore
                    , n = this.scrollYStore
                    , r = t.tableBody
                    , i = t.rightBody
                    , o = t.tableFooter
                    , a = r ? r.$el : null
                    , s = i ? i.$el : null
                    , c = o ? o.$el : null;
                return s && ((0,
                    l.restoreScrollListener)(s),
                    s.scrollTop = 0),
                c && (c.scrollLeft = 0),
                a && ((0,
                    l.restoreScrollListener)(a),
                    a.scrollTop = 0,
                    a.scrollLeft = 0),
                    e.startIndex = 0,
                    n.startIndex = 0,
                    this.$nextTick()
            },
            updateFooter: function() {
                var t = this.showFooter
                    , e = this.visibleColumn
                    , n = this.footerMethod;
                return t && n && (this.footerTableData = e.length ? n({
                    columns: e,
                    data: this.afterFullData,
                    $table: this,
                    $grid: this.$xegrid
                }) : []),
                    this.$nextTick()
            },
            updateStatus: function(t, e) {
                var n = this
                    , i = !r.default.isUndefined(e);
                return this.$nextTick().then((function() {
                        var r = n.$refs
                            , o = n.editRules
                            , a = n.validStore;
                        if (t && r.tableBody && o) {
                            var s = t.row
                                , l = t.column
                                , c = "change";
                            if (n.hasCellRules(c, s, l)) {
                                var u = n.getCell(s, l);
                                if (u)
                                    return n.validCellRules(c, s, l, e).then((function() {
                                            i && a.visible && C(s, l, e),
                                                n.clearValidate()
                                        }
                                    )).catch((function(t) {
                                            var r = t.rule;
                                            i && C(s, l, e),
                                                n.showValidTooltip({
                                                    rule: r,
                                                    row: s,
                                                    column: l,
                                                    cell: u
                                                })
                                        }
                                    ))
                            }
                        }
                    }
                ))
            },
            handleDefaultMergeCells: function() {
                this.setMergeCells(this.mergeCells)
            },
            setMergeCells: function(t) {
                var e = this;
                return this.spanMethod && s.UtilTools.error("vxe.error.errConflicts", ["merge-cells", "span-method"]),
                    U(this, t, this.mergeList, this.afterFullData),
                    this.$nextTick().then((function() {
                            return e.updateCellAreas()
                        }
                    ))
            },
            removeMergeCells: function(t) {
                var e = this;
                this.spanMethod && s.UtilTools.error("vxe.error.errConflicts", ["merge-cells", "span-method"]);
                var n = Y(this, t, this.mergeList, this.afterFullData);
                return this.$nextTick().then((function() {
                        return e.updateCellAreas(),
                            n
                    }
                ))
            },
            getMergeCells: function() {
                return this.mergeList.slice(0)
            },
            clearMergeCells: function() {
                return this.mergeList = [],
                    this.$nextTick()
            },
            handleDefaultMergeFooterItems: function() {
                this.setMergeFooterItems(this.mergeFooterItems)
            },
            setMergeFooterItems: function(t) {
                var e = this;
                return this.footerSpanMethod && s.UtilTools.error("vxe.error.errConflicts", ["merge-footer-items", "footer-span-method"]),
                    U(this, t, this.mergeFooterList, null),
                    this.$nextTick().then((function() {
                            return e.updateCellAreas()
                        }
                    ))
            },
            removeMergeFooterItems: function(t) {
                var e = this;
                this.footerSpanMethod && s.UtilTools.error("vxe.error.errConflicts", ["merge-footer-items", "footer-span-method"]);
                var n = Y(this, t, this.mergeFooterList, null);
                return this.$nextTick().then((function() {
                        return e.updateCellAreas(),
                            n
                    }
                ))

                    return this[this.vertical ? "computedHeight" : "computedWidth"]

                    return this.count * this.size
                },

                    return (this.active + this.count) % this.count

                    var t = this.vertical ? "vertical" : "horizontal";
                    return this.direction === t

                    }
                    return t
                },

                    return {
                        backgroundColor: this.indicatorColor
                    }
                },

                    return (this.vertical ? this.rect.height : this.rect.width) - this.size * this.count
                }
